ght; surely now he would awake for thee, and make the habitation of thy righteousness prosperous.","year":-1520},{"id":"recJpQQz0BZTQ3qiT","ref":"Job.8.7","text":"Though thy beginning was small, yet thy latter end should greatly increase.","year":-1520},{"id":"recyhvScZaqDxHCCN","ref":"Job.8.8","text":"For enquire, I pray thee, of the former age, and prepare thyself to the search of their fathers:","year":-1520}]}
